divs: sighting detailsat 11:20 my brother said come and check this out knowing that i am interested in anything out of place in the sky.i went out side and we watched an object that looked like a string or row of lights that moved left to right, up and down changing from a row of lights to a single light changing color and very bright, colors included blue red yellow purple green, this was not a helicopter plane satellite, space station or star, i got my camera and took pictures, i watched this object for 43 mins until it went down\landed at 12:03am, at the time i was on face book until he got me to come have a look at this out of place site,this was a ufo.ps you may have to zoom in on the pictures to see more clearly. thanks and warm regards *(wit's first name deleted--cms\sg). for more pictures or details contact me on **(wit's email address deleted -- cms\sg).
